instruction: Name a few famous public figures from the 1980s in the US.
output:
1. Ronald Reagan - 40th President of the United States
2. Mikhail Gorbachev - General Secretary of the Communist Party of the Soviet Union
3. Bill Cosby - Comic and actor
4. Steve Jobs - Co-founder of Apple Inc.
5. Michael Jackson - Singer and pop superstar
6. George H. W. Bush - 41st President of the United States
7. Oprah Winfrey - Talk show host and television producer
8. Madonna - Singer and songwriter
9. Margaret Thatcher - Prime Minister of the United Kingdom
10. Tom Cruise - Actor and producer.
